<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53001541/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Along the course there will be provided some homework activities and/or exercises to be done during the class.
These activities will allow the students to increase their final grade up to 2 points.
All the students must do the final written examination.
